Product Benefits

Why Thermacool works — concise benefits and real-world value for athletes, workers, and everyday use.

Long-lasting Cooling

Phase-change material (PCM) pockets provide up to 2–4 hours of passive cooling per recharge, reducing heat stress during activity.

Lightweight & Breathable

Made from 80% recycled polyester with breathable mesh channels so you stay comfortable without bulk.

Sustainable Design

Durable construction and fully recyclable materials reduce lifecycle waste compared to disposable cooling products.

Easy Care

Machine washable outer layers; PCM packs are removable and recharged using water or refrigeration depending on the model.

Performance & Recovery

Lower skin temperature and perceived exertion during workouts, and faster cooling for post-exertion recovery.

Versatile Use

Ideal for sports, outdoor work, travel, and everyday wear in hot climates — available in shirts, polos, and accessory packs.

About Thermacool

Founded by three partners in Penrith, Australia, Thermacool brings professional-grade cooling to everyday apparel. Our shirts use phase‑change materials (PCM) to absorb heat and regulate body temperature—battery‑free and reusable.

  • 80% recycled polyester; 100% recyclable
  • Passive cooling up to 3 hours
  • Cost‑based pricing to stay affordable

Our Mission

We aim to redefine cooling apparel by integrating advanced PCM technology into lightweight, stylish, and eco‑friendly shirts—helping people stay fresh, confident, and productive at work, in sport, and in daily life.
